{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000230", "chronotag": "1739874524455", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CL230", "numeroOrdreDepot": "230", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B0134", "triAmendement": "boaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaf", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA794466", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845470", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA267780", "PA841833", "PA720908"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Moulliere,  Mme&#160;Firmin&#160;Le&#160;Bodo, M.&#160;Guerin et Mme&#160;Moutchou"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 6", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 6", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 6", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0134.asp#D_Article_6"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>R&#x00E9;diger ainsi cet article&nbsp;:</p><p>&#x00AB;&nbsp;Le dernier alin&#x00E9;a de l&#x2019;article L.&nbsp;511&#x2011;1 du code de la s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9; int&#x00E9;rieure est compl&#x00E9;t&#x00E9; par une phrase ainsi r&#x00E9;dig&#x00E9;e&nbsp;: &#x00AB;&nbsp;Les communes associent les op&#x00E9;rateurs de transport &#x00E0; la conclusion de cette convention.&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Les signatures de conventions entre les op&#x00E9;rateurs de transport et les communes ou EPCI sont d&#x2019;ores et d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; en train de se multiplier. Outre la facult&#x00E9; d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; existante pour les communes contigu&#x00EB;s desservies par un ou plusieurs r&#x00E9;seaux de transports publics de conclure une convention locale de s&#x00FB;ret&#x00E9; des transports collectifs, des conventions sign&#x00E9;es au cas par cas s&#x2019;&#x00E9;laborent donc d&#x2019;ores et d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0;.</p><p>Il appara&#x00EE;t n&#x00E9;anmoins n&#x00E9;cessaire que ces conventions associent syst&#x00E9;matiquement les op&#x00E9;rateurs de transports afin d&#x2019;am&#x00E9;liorer la coordination entre les diff&#x00E9;rents acteurs et d&#x2019;assurer l&#x2019;efficacit&#x00E9; du continuum de s&#x00E9;curit&#x00E9;.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-23", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-27T15:45:37+01:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000230?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "74498", "typePosition": "Dernier"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}